#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor crowbar'}
#: .\surv_crowbar_tools.json
msgid ""
"A combat crow bar carefully adjusted in shape and weight balance. Various "
"practical improvements such as hand guards and non-conductive grips have "
"been made, and the open performance has also been improved compared to "
"normal bars."
msgstr "一把經過精心調整形狀與重量平衡的戰鬥撬棍。進行了護手與非導電握把等多種實用改進，其撬開性能相比普通撬棍也有所提升。"
